org.xlattice.corexml.expr

Class AxisName

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.corexml.expr.AxisName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FixedNameToken, Token

    public class AxisName
extends java.lang.Object
implements FixedNameToken
    A token representing an XPath 1.0 axis name.

    NOTE that the String names use underscores (_) instead of dashes (-).

    Author:
    Jim Dixon
